"\"<div>This dual-workshop experience is designed to develop well-rounded, people-first leaders who can drive results while cultivating a thriving work culture.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div><b>In Sales Leadership in Action<\/b>, participants will gain practical tools to lead high-performing sales teams by building trust, aligning goals, and driving accountability. The session focuses on real-world strategies that empower leaders to inspire and influence with impact.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div><b>In Happy Teams, Healthy Results<\/b>, the focus shifts to the heart of organizational success\u2014employee well-being. Participants will explore how to recognize and reduce burnout, create psychologically safe environments, and implement wellness-centered practices that boost morale and productivity.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Together, these workshops provide a holistic leadership approach that connects performance with purpose, and results with relationships\u2014equipping today\u2019s leaders to succeed through both strategy and empathy.<\/div><div><br><\/div>\""